author: Bruce Jenkins
title: Cal Bears lose a thriller in Utah, 30-24
text:
Photo: Rick Bowmer, AP California quarterback Jared Goff (16) passes the ball in the first half during an NCAA college football game against Utah, Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Salt Lake City. California quarterback Jared Goff (16) passes the ball in the first...
Gathered at an outdoor podium with hundreds of cheering Utah students in the background, ESPN’s “Game Day” crew made it a clean sweep in its pregame predictions in Salt Lake City Saturday morning. Everyone, including ex-collegiate stars Desmond Howard and Kirk Herbstreit, picked the 5th-ranked Utes to beat Cal.
